data.value: 1) Any carton Qty diff. automatically needs replenishment. 2) Part I audit is under Pull iPacks. 3) Part II audit is under Pull Cartons. 4) Functional Test of Elongation, Moulding, Bonding & Lamination is not necessary. 5) For Defect details with description is shown on supplement sheet. 6) Each project qty must be packed on separate carton.
